summary: The agent report accurately identifies the root cause and provides logical reasoning, but lacks detail in the causal chain and specific metrics. Suggested actions are relevant but could be more detailed.

dimensions.name: Root Cause Accuracy
dimensions.explanation: The agent correctly identified CM as the root cause of the VCORE increase.

dimensions.name: Causal Chain Completeness

dimensions.name: Metric Precision
dimensions.explanation: Most metrics are correctly identified, but some specific DDR percentages are missing.

dimensions.name: Reasoning Quality
dimensions.explanation: The reasoning is logical and correctly rules out MMDVFS, but lacks detail on CPU and DDR.

dimensions.name: Actionability
